original_title: A/Level Practical tests for engineering technology subject tomorrow
original_body_lines: COLOMBO(News 1st): The Department of Examinations says that the practical tests related to the engineering technology subject of the 2022 A/level examination will start from tomorrow.
Its spokesperson Lasika Samarakoon says that the practicals will commence on the 21st of July.
For further information, you can contact the Department of Examinations on their Hotline 1911.
The practical tests related to the subjects of oriental music and dancing ended on July 6th.
